msgid ""
"While we wait, I'll quickly show you another useful feature. All "
"construction\n"
"sites look the same and some buildings look alike. It is sometimes hard to "
"tell\n"
"them apart. Widelands offers a feature to show label texts over the "
"buildings.\n"
